				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I have a lvl 44 pally on Povar and use a Sarnak battle shield along with a Wurmslayer very effectively. I get bashes several times each fight for up to 57 each and averaging probably around 30 to 40 each. My Wurmy (1hs) hits for up to 100 and probably averages in 60's or 70's per hit. Don't underestimate the stun you often get with bashing or the ability to interupt spells cast against you by mobs, it helps a lot! 2hs weaps look very good, but any that are better than my wurmslayer are either prohibitively expensive or have an even higher delay than the the 40 on my wurmy! I think the added armor of 25ac 40hp fire 10 and cold 10 and magic 10 protection of my shield is also very nice! Until I find a 2hs or 2hb weapon that imo works better, I will stay with what I have. Or until I get a better epic weapon than my Ghoulbane. 
